                %li If you choose to find your friends (iii) through a search of names or usernames on MetaFad then simply type a name to search and we will perform a search on our Service.
            %li 
              %b Analytics information:
              %ul 
                %li We use third-party analytics tools to help us measure traffic and usage trends for the Service. These tools collect information sent by your device or our Service, including the web pages you visit, add-ons, and other information that assists us in improving the Service. We collect and use this analytics information with analytics information from other Users so that it cannot reasonably be used to identify any particular individual User.
            %li 
